.TH TWSU-DETAILS 1 "July 2026" "tw-safe-update 1.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
twsu-details \- show the last update verdict with the full change list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B twsu-details
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints the last saved verdict from
.BR twsu-check (1)
including every package and Flatpak that would change (equivalent to
.B twsu-check --pretty --cached --list
), then waits for Enter. Launched by the tray's \(lqDetails\(rq button.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR twsu-check (1),
.BR twsu-tray (1)
